cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SI, cs.PF 

This paper deals with the performance analysis of caching systems in computer networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the impact of temporal and geographical locality on cache performance, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and social networks (cs.SI). Finally, the paper presents a simple traffic model that can be used for analytical and simulative studies of caching systems, which is a topic related to performance analysis (cs.PF).
